Task: 08
Title: Ensemble orchestration and config
Phase: 2
Route: full
Slice: Panel Fan-out + Synthesis, Judge Analysis
Dependencies: 07
Scope: Modify RunFusionUseCase to orchestrate the full ensemble pipeline — PanelRunner.run() → JudgeStep.analyze() → SynthesizeStep.synthesize() — yielding progress, content_delta, and done FusionStreamEvents. Implement graceful degradation: judge failure omits analysis and synthesis proceeds with raw panel responses. Expand fusion.config.json with multiple panel providers (role: "panel"), one judge provider (role: "judge"), and one synthesizer provider (role: "synthesizer"). The use case's cross-phase modification (originally created in Task 03) replaces the passthrough logic with the ensemble sequence.
Acceptance Criteria: AC-7, AC-8, AC-9
NFRs: NFR-1, NFR-5
Gate Criteria: Phase 2 Gate 1 (response references panel and judge content), Phase 2 Gate 2 (judge-unreachable graceful degradation verified)
Files:
  - src/application/usecases/run-fusion-use-case.ts (MODIFY) — Replace passthrough with orchestrated sequence: PanelRunner.run() → JudgeStep.analyze() (with graceful degradation) → SynthesizeStep.synthesize(); yield progress, content_delta, done events; wire LoggerPort for judge failure logging; pass optional Analysis to SynthesizeStep
  - fusion.config.json (MODIFY) — Expand providers array: multiple role: "panel" entries, one role: "judge" entry, one role: "synthesizer" entry
